Description
-----------

This CVar allows for the user to drag moveable objects around in game
using the mouse.

Usage
-----

At the console type...

    g_dragEntity [int]

Parameters
----------

-   [int] - Enables/Disables the dragging of movable objects.
    -   0 - Turns this feature off.
    -   1 - Turns this feature on.

